  ('optician-moex-02679', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '夜間配戴之角膜塑型隱形眼鏡材質，一般最常用為下列何者？', '["水膠（hydrogels）", "矽水膠（silicone hydrogels）", "氟矽丙烯酸酯（fluoro-silicone/acrylates）", "聚甲基丙烯酸甲酯（polymethylmethacrylate, PMMA）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21dccecf40fb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "332b43e00546", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02680', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據Holden and Mertz（1984）的研究，要減少和避免角膜水腫，長戴型的軟式隱形眼鏡（extending wear soft contact lenses），其鏡片傳氧率（Dk/L）至少必須達到：', '["24", "32", "45", "87"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21dccecf40fb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "332b43e00546", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02681', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是隱形眼鏡保養液常用的滅菌主成分？', '["玻尿酸（hyaluronan）", "聚季銨鹽（polyquad）", "聚氨基丙基雙胍（polyaminopropyl biguanide）", "聚六亞甲基雙胍（polyhexamethylene biguanide）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21dccecf40fb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "332b43e00546", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02682', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於隱形眼鏡護理方式，下列敘述何者正確？', '["應先完成眼妝後，再配戴隱形眼鏡", "應先使用髮膠香水後，再配戴隱形眼鏡", "應先卸妝清潔後，再取出隱形眼鏡", "自製生理食鹽水可有效清潔隱形眼鏡"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21dccecf40fb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "332b43e00546", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02683', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '隱形眼鏡材質的選擇，需考量患者配戴時間長短、屈光情形及眼表面健康。下列鏡片選擇敘述，何者錯 誤？', '["輕微過敏性結膜炎患者，最近眼分泌物多，應選擇表面高親水性的鏡片材料，以避免蛋白沉澱", "淚水分泌不足乾眼（tear deficiency dry eye）患者，配戴隱形眼鏡時，鏡片容易脫水，短時間配戴可選 擇含水量相對低或不易脫水的材質", "高度遠視患者若長時間配戴隱形眼鏡，應儘量使用高透氧材質，以避免因鏡片中心較厚，降低氧氣通透", "當患者因反覆性角膜糜爛（recurrent corneal erosion）需使用治療型隱形眼鏡（therapeutic contact lens） 連續配戴多日，應選擇高透氧材質"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21dccecf40fb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "332b43e00546", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
